                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9116" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0271</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1666 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工程机械龙头，混改助力问鼎全球</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Construction Machinery Leader, Mixed-Ownership Reform Aids in Climbing to the Global Summit</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贾良定，王彦，张薇，宁鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐工集团工程机械股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">27 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国企混改；异质资本；资本生态系统；价值共生；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">State-owned Enterprise (SOE) Mixed-Ownership Reform; Heterogeneous Capital; Capital Ecosystem; Value Co-creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业的混合所有制改革具有资本动员的属性，旨在推动国有资本和国有企业做优做强做大，畅通国民经济循环，促进各种所有制经济优势互补、共同发展。徐工有限是徐工集团内历史最悠久且业务最核心的成员企业，是江苏省首批混合所有制改革试点企业。其混改以引进战略投资者为契机，切实提升企业的功能价值与核心竞争力，打造了“红色基因+光荣传统+先进机制”的新模式，参与混改的异质资本间达成动态平衡，实现经济属性、政治属性、社会属性的有机统一。并形成“国企控股＋民企参股＋核心骨干持股”的三方利益共同体，实现混改资本的价值共生，徐工有限的深度混改成为业界标杆。本案例以徐工有限的混改动因、路径及效果为主线，将其视为一个资本生态系统，对异质资本所处的生态位、组织惯性的后果以及混改实现价值共生的路径进行分析，重点探讨异质股东的冲突特征、异质资本如何平衡发展等问题。旨在通过案例学习让学生初步掌握国有企业混改、混合所有制经济及组织生态学知识，了解公司治理、组织合法性与共生理论等相关内容，为混改企业如何通过异质资本间的嵌入实现价值共生提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The mixed-ownership reform of state-owned enterprises has the attribute of capital mobilization, aiming to promote the optimization, strengthening, and expansion of state-owned capital and enterprises, unblocking the circulation of the national economy, and promoting the complementary development of various forms of ownership economy. XCMG is the oldest and most core member enterprise of XCMG Group, and was one of the first pilot enterprises for mixed-ownership reform in Jiangsu Province. Its mixed-ownership reform took the opportunity of introducing strategic investors to enhance the functional value and core competitiveness of the enterprise, and created a new model of &quot;red gene + glorious tradition + advanced mechanism&quot;. The heterogeneous capital participating in the mixed-ownership reform achieved dynamic balance, and realized the organic unity of economic attributes, political attributes, and social attributes. It also formed a tripartite interest community of &quot;state-owned enterprises holding the majority stake, private enterprises participating, and core staff holding shares&quot;, and achieved the value symbiosis of mixed-ownership capital. XCMG deeps mixed-ownership reform has become a benchmark in the industry. This case takes XCMG&#39;s mixed-ownership reform as the main line, regards it as a capital ecosystem, analyzes the ecological niches of heterogeneous capital, the consequences of organizational habits, and the paths to achieving value symbiosis, focusing on the conflict characteristics of heterogeneous shareholders and how heterogeneous capital can achieve balanced development. The aim is to enable students to acquire basic knowledge of mixed-ownership reform, mixed-ownership economy, and organizational ecology, understand the related content of corporate governance, organizational legitimacy, and symbiosis theory, and provide reference for mixed-ownership reform enterprises on how to achieve value symbiosis through the embedding of heterogeneous capital.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织生态学；共生理论；合法性</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
